column5: Don,t get me wrong ,I love to catch fish,probably more than most, but fishing trips are more than just that.Here are a few pictures from last year of things I love the most about fishing besides big fish.........             Happy New Year and good fishing for 2010....
Great pics Larry and very nice seeing you on the river in '09. You have a super year......healthy and happy. The rest always falls into place.
Love the pic of the bass boat. Mission control, Ready for take off.
Very nice, Larry, those are some great shots.  A Happy New Year to ya.
Wadda trophy! I topped my pb seagull this year.
300 Hp   HOLLY sufferin sucafash  Comes with parachutes too right ?
